channel.title: My first graphic ever made with photoshop
channel.description:
Hello guys, I ever started with photoshop 3 years ago. My friend didnt wanted his license anymore and gived it to me. So i wanted to try some things in photoshop , new things i never know they were there. this was what i made : [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/2415wk2.jpg[/img] This was my first graphic , If u see its all Abstract. I worked my first designs out in a theme , this one was Abstract... But i stopped for two years cuz school and a half year ago i picked the license up and started back (I found this graphic on my old hard disk)
Regards, ~Ircdscape (Sorry for my bad english ;D )
